# Ignore everything by default. This workspace contains personal files,
# course materials, generated archives, and CAD outputs that should not be
# published accidentally.
*

# Keep directories traversable for explicit allow rules.
!*/

# Repository metadata and docs.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!AGENTS.md
!CONTEXT.md
!docs/
!docs/**

# GitHub Pages deployment.
!.github/
!.github/**

# Clean static website package for publishing.
!企业管理自测站-上线包/
!企业管理自测站-上线包/**

# Editable source copies for the static site.
!企业管理/
!企业管理/index.html
!企业管理/企业管理自测练习网页.html
!企业管理/题库格式转换器.html
!企业管理/题库模板.json

# Always ignore common temporary/generated files even inside allowed folders.
**/~$*
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
**/*.log
**/*.zip
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
